17
00:02:00,366 --> 00:02:02,000
Tong Il must be his fetal nickname.

18
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,133
Are you having a son?

19
00:02:03,133 --> 00:02:04,933
Yes, it's a son.

20
00:02:04,933 --> 00:02:06,333
Big sister.

21
00:02:07,166 --> 00:02:08,633
Eat these eggs.

22
