24
00:02:13,166 --> 00:02:14,333
Try this, too.

25
00:02:14,333 --> 00:02:16,733
It's a meal kit
made with 100 percent Korean produce.

26
00:02:16,733 --> 00:02:18,233
It's popular these days.

27
00:02:18,233 --> 00:02:21,466
I've tried that. I highly recommend it.

28
00:02:21,466 --> 00:02:22,900
Am I in the video, too?

29
