Yes, you can watch it
on my social media account later.

30
00:02:32,833 --> 00:02:33,866
Hello.

31
00:02:33,866 --> 00:02:35,200
Welcome, Gyeong Ho.

32
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,533
It's really good.

33
00:02:44,533 --> 00:02:45,666
You have to try it.

34
00:02:45,666 --> 00:02:47,233
Is that so?

35
